{"tid":1238851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大公話林鄭會道歉撤回方案個社論del咗","createTime":"2019-06-18T03:18:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T03:23:40.000Z","uid":50386,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9eacf700349c2ad934308dd5e39a9017dcf9fc22","tid":1238851,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:18:56.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥上周六宣佈暫緩《逃犯條例》修訂，但未能平息市民怒火，繼續要求政府將條例完全撤回、撤銷6.12對示威者的控罪，以及林鄭下台等，在周日200萬人上街後，林鄭以書面向市民道歉，但並無現身。林鄭今日將會見傳媒，據《大公報》今日社評指，估計林鄭今日將會宣布正式撤回條例草案及再度作出「誠摯」道歉，形容「這是一種非常謙卑和認真的處事態度，顯示的是為政者應有的道德勇氣和責任承擔，值得給予理解和支持」。但其後在《大公報》網頁，此篇社評的連結已失效，文章被刪去，只餘下﻿標題「支持林鄭依法施政 發展經濟改善民生」，但未能觀看內容。<br />\n<br />\n柒婆想縮<br />\n上面唔比佢縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160c0494825d71d142b71c707e2b66a475f93321","tid":1238851,"uid":219211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:19:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71611510a8b73a051c5933fb22fc33ae85f57f50","tid":1238851,"uid":258927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:19:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U4rguvu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU4rguvu.jpg&h=f7216136&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n# 生於亂世 有種責任<br />\n# 求share出fb/ig/tg/wtsapp"},{"pid":"ec77366f526f5d71a2393361b1a1aa68da9ed8ef","tid":1238851,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:20:06.000Z","msg":"證明上面都鬥得好勁"},{"pid":"d28bd89d966ee410721e5fb6a1963ced3718d4e1","tid":1238851,"uid":219277,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:21:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e5c15db9d5876207220edfef7a007c59187139","tid":1238851,"uid":231523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:23:40.000Z","msg":"又 改口風"}]}